Hello, and welcome to Burgos, the to-be cutting-edge distributed ftp indexer and search engine !

Latest version is available at https://launchpad.net/burgos

This software is governed by the CeCILL license. You can find the full license in the file COPYING (or COPYING.fr for the french version).

See INSTALL for instructions on how to build Burgos from source.

Please remember that this software is curently under development, and therefore it may not work perfectly. Please report any bug to our bug tracking system : https://bugs.launchpad.net/burgos
